(Sundiata Post) — Embattled Senator Dino Melaye representing Kogi West senatorial district on the platform of the All Progressives Congress (APC) resumed in the Senate this morning and has defected to the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP). He announced his defection on the floor of the Senate on Wednesday morning which caused confusion as APC and PDP senators exchanged words over the defection. It was reported that Dino Melaye appeared in a neck brace and was seated near the former Senate President, David Mark. Details shortly…